MOST IMMEDIATE
No.1/34/1/2002-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR).
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 11th January, 2002
21 Pausa, 1923 (S)
The undersigned is directed to state that consequent upon the merger of
the Ministry of Communications and Ministry of Information Technology and
creation of a new Ministry, namely, the Ministry of Communications and
Information Technology, the following Ministers are redesignated as under :-
i)
Shri Pramod Mahajan Minister of Communications and Information
Technology.
He will continue to hold the charge of the office of
Minister of Parliamentary Affairs.
ii) Shri Tapan Sikdar
Minister
of
State
in
the
Ministry
of
Communications and Information Technology.
(P. Gbpalakrishnan)
for Cabinet Secretary.
Tele : 3015802
To
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded for information to Deputy Chairman and Members of
the Planning Commission.
(P. Gopalakrishnan)
for Cabinet Secretary.

Secretary to the Vice-President.
(P. Gopalakrishnan)
